License: ASL 2.0
Vendor: EMI
URL: http://glite.cern.ch/
Group: Applications/Internet
BuildArch: %{_arch}
Requires: glite-wms-configuration glite-wms-helper glite-wms-ism glite-wms-purger glite-wms-common glite-lb-client
Requires(post): chkconfig
